TITLE: Episode 23 - Black Magic Woman [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: What was your crystalizing moment? What moment pushed you towards liberty and made you realize that you weren’t a Republican or a Democrat, but rather a libertarian? Mine was a speech by Dr. Paul. Today, Cam spends some time talking about what that moment would look like today, would could create that moment, and what that person should say.
